<br>
Weighty Polearm   <br>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM  <br>
Damage: 29<br>
Delay: 34 <br>
Ratio: 1.172 Amazing <br>
AC: +15 Agi: +15 Fire Resist: +10 HP: +35  <br>
Weight: 9.5 <br>
Weapon Skill: Two Hand Slash <br>
Classes: Warrior Shadowknight Paladin Ranger  <br>
Races: All Races  <br>
 <br>
Its super common, has a damn low price (250 on Druzzil), and it has a better ratio than alot of other popular 2hs.  Better than a BaH, and Strength of Grodan.  Plus the stats that go with it are an added bonus, 15 ac is kick ass, along with 15 agility, 10 fire resist, and even 35 HP.  People must not like it because they can't give it to there twink, boohoo.  Untill I win a roll on a windblade, you can see my stubby ass wielding a huge stick with a little axe head.<br>
<br>
<br>
Traxx Warrdorf<br>
